Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jyukuro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you open the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be bad for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy... \NHow is he? {???}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Mizusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's annoying.\NHow many times do you need to try{make sure}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, didn't you think it would be nice \Nif we all simply lost this power altogether? {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{How is it? Is Saeko better?}So? Is Saeko better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's out of the woods now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you wait here for so long. {I'm sorry to keep you both up until this late. \NThank you. I'll handle it from here on.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'll handle it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Had we been showered\N in his light at the park back then,{If we had been showered \Nin his light there at the park,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd both have ended up\N bedridden together with Saeko.{we'd both end up \Nbedridden together with Saeko.} {intentional}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ki-san, you're so dirty! {for this - he implies a threesome}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, information like that is something you'd want to know in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Jyukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiga-san didn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to watch {\i1}him{\i0} closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess Shinobu \Ndidn't know everything either?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the more important\N something is, the more we try to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Neutralizer? {中和能力者}{so the jp wiki thing says that these kanji are read as the titular Aurabuster (though of course she doesn't pronounce them that way). Not sure if there is a way to show this in the line}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say, but...{You say "you wasn't," but...} {either this or "you weren't" - you wasn't is about as grammatical as word here going}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for you \Nblaming Miga's death on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, did it come across that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't helping it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of Kunaki-sama's revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a small price to pay, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What troubles me is that he fell into King Kara's lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least now we know for sure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if our little boy \Nis going to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be fine for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it was him \Nwho failed to protect Miga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That spoiled Young General...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's losing a subordinate or two \Nif it's to fulfill Kunaki-sama's request?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for him to regret his carelessness.{It's already too late to warn \Nthe kid about being careful.} {?????}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, he'll pay for it with his own life. {???}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's Kanbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sakiya-kun? \NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NBe there in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Did I make you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NWhy are you shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:32.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,And then, when that woman burned to a crisp, \Nshe turned into a beautiful stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,That stone was then eaten by a black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember exactly what happened after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel like I had seen\N the same scene long ago.{but I feel like I saw \Nthe same scene from long ago.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Same scene? Deja vu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't think so.\NI can't say why, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:08:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always been hard for me to tell the illusions and reality apart until after the fact{much later}. {meaning "after it was over"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I dumped this at you all at once... \NThere's no way you'll believe me.{Surely enough, you won't believe me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire coming out of a hand, \Nswords crushing on the barrier of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like science fiction novel stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't believe a word...{You usually wouldn't take it at face value...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't you, Sakiya-kun! {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so pleased!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Called me on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This late at night.{At such an hour.} {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just needed someone to hear me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it me who you decided to call \Non the spur of the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun if you become uneasy,{Sakiya-kun, you often get uneasy,}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you get worried,{you often get worried,}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ever feel like that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,don't hesitate to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, before anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I know for sure is that we can't let his power fall into their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he our trump card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels more like a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to concern ourselves \Nwith thinking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we catch him \Nand drag him to Saiga Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, Ki-sama will be paying\N 8,000 yen a day for the hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think he's that powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not like your usual self, Ki-san. \NI think we're past the stage of doubting it. {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisara, don't brood on it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizusawa, pay attention to his surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say you want me to stand watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisara will replace you when night comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone comes and pesters me, \Ncan I knock his face in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to follow your orders.{Maintain the order at all times.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun, got any plans \Nfor the afternoon today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should be free. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was hoping you'd go shopping with me.{Well, I'd be happy to have you \Ngo shopping with me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to a Big Mac. Let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this why you brought me along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{We've only one more place to go. Deal?}There's only one more store I want to check out. Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "Deal" me in this situation! {lit: not nee}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just take a look at what's there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get extra pocket money or something? \NThis stereo system is top of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I recently broke the CD tray \Non the one I have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might as well buy it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that didn't matter \Nto me all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to listen to your story.{I just wanted to talk to you.} {?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wanted you to tell me! {don't really know what's the difference}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{The continuation of yesterday's story...}I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened after what you told me, what you're thinking about right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Like what you're thinking right now, \Nand what you're going to do!}and what you're planning to do now! Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know.{All I want is to know it...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If... possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you have this in size nine.{the ninth size.} {guessing it's about size}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Size nine, ma'am? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is size nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, silly me! \NCould you wrap it up for me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, stop distracting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met them ever since I was little. {?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I must also be one of them. {?? maybe "I was sure everyone is like that"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Being like them, having abilities that set me apart from regular people...{They have abilities \Nthat set them apart from regular people. }{???}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It sickens me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just seeing and sensing them,\Nwho are not like the rest of the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that...{That alone...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ki-san told me you wanted to see me... {satomi is jyukuro, the glasses guy}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That sly Ki-san! {/liar}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jyukuro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizusawa, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... How did I end up shopping on this assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm saying \Nthat I only need a moment with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not planning to do anything to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that I'm gonna \Nhave to force you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rude! You just come up and\N make demands without explanation!{It's rude! You just come up \Nand demand something for no reason!} {lit: without explaining anything, suddenly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd ever agree \Nto follow someone like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just leave me alone already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what you people are fighting for,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and frankly, I don't want \Nto have anything to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late. {meaning he's already involved?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no going back for you anymore! {/to yesterday}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how you do it, Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop trying to force him! {/don't act violentlya}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want your precious princess \Nto be dragged into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why did you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've definitely done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you get lost real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing{prepared} to let you go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need that for? {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To chop your head off! {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How impertinent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Heart—one sword. {idk what her power is, the wiki doesn't have it}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be over soon.{Don't get too used to it.} {??????} {raku ni nareru yo -> you're going to die}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisara! Don't fall for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was... an illusion? {?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A mere psychic is able to resist it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive that you saw right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To give credit where it's due.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is showing some lousy illusions \Nthe best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My Suzaku sword is a lot more real!{But my Suzaku sword is very real!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, Mizusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just another one of her illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The real one is probably with Sakiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Why does it have to be so complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Covering the whole mall with the barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jyukuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,Don't let her trick you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:31.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,You should be able to see through it.{You would definitely know...} {?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai-chan, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your plan?! \NWhy is Ai-chan now involved too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A single "Thank you" wouldn't go amiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not bad for a psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce myself.{Let's introduce ourselves.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of the Three Demon Generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Phantom General Kou! {幻将・皓}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider this information a present for the afterlife.{I'll take you to the underworld as my souvenir.} {??????? assuming meido here is 冥土 but i still dk what she means}{her telling him her name is her 冥土の土産 to him, i.e. she's about to kill him}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are quite something!{You're a real deal!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're faced with a\N stronger barrier, you'll die!{But your barrier is only as strong as you are!} {??????} {not sure what the last word is, shinuna?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, psychic, you narrowly \Nescaped with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jyukuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Three Demon Generals?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First the Flame General, \Nnow the Phantom General Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of him... {?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he hesitating? {???????}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even want \Nto hear anything about it. {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can give you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:30.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,Despite all that commotion, \NI feel like nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:35.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even those {scars}wounds have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:38.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even though I still remember how they hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want my parents to notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, my dude, \Nwhat's there to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:22:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just play along and help us \Ncrush those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!{Please go away!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cold to me, dude! \NThat's no way to talk to a friend. {not really}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you give it a rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand you're bothering him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think \Nyou can just come here?! {lit: what did you come for unconcernedly; nonchalantly; shamelessly; brazenly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't want to drag you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna start a fight here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and let him see your true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to kill our kind and eat our life orbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want \Nto get him involved for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true? Are your motives really that vile?{Is that true? \NSuch savagery is among your methods too?} {/doing such savage; barbarous; barbaric things}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret this, Suguro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of things I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:23:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.13,0:24:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you... {??}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.97,0:24:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd both prefer not to have this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.97,0:24:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.45,0:24:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well played.
