Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.63,0:00:39.42,Song,,0,0,0,,The heat haze of times immemorial\Nreflects the melody of the Milky Way, {太古(いにしえ)の陽炎(かげろう)が\N映(は)ゆる銀河(みなも)の音律(しらべ)\N貴方(あなた)が歩む軌跡(あしどり)\Nその眼差し　永遠を希(もと)め}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.67,0:00:52.85,Song,,0,0,0,,The path you walk, \Nyour gaze, yearning for eternity
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.85,0:01:04.94,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, I've been waiting for you here \Nall this time, all these years {愛しい人よ\N今まで待ち続けたここで}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.94,0:01:13.93,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll be watching you from now on and forever, \Njust as if we're snuggling up, {これからずっと\N見つめてるよ\Nただ寄り添うように\N零(ゼロ)に還ってゆく\Nその日まで}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.93,0:01:21.29,Song,,0,0,0,,until the day you return to zero
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.26,0:24:55.66,Song,,0,0,0,,Come here and open the window {ここにおいで 窓をあけてくれたら\Nめぐりあえる 出会いと約束}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.71,0:25:03.13,Song,,0,0,0,,and we'll meet and make a promise
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.67,0:25:10.57,Song,,0,0,0,,The truth I saw in the corner of the classroom {教室の片隅で見た\Nほんとのこと\Nだれにも言えないリアルもあるさ}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:10.57,0:25:16.98,Song,,0,0,0,,There are also some real things I can't tell anyone
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.85,0:25:21.06,Song,,0,0,0,,Searchin' angel night {Searchin' angel night\N扉の奥\N隠れてた愛が\Nflyin' on flyin' out めざめだす\NCallin' birth of light\N優しさだけ\Nとどくよ きみの 心へ...}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.40,0:25:24.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Behind the door
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.43,0:25:29.61,Song,,0,0,0,,The hidden love
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.61,0:25:33.28,Song,,0,0,0,,Flyin' on flyin' out, it's awakening
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.28,0:25:35.87,Song,,0,0,0,,Callin' birth of light
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.66,0:25:39.57,Song,,0,0,0,,Only kindness
Dialogue: 10,0:25:40.67,0:25:47.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Will reach your heart
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.44,0:26:08.11,Song,,0,0,0,,What remains the same as we grow up? {大人になって 変わらないものは何?\N悩んだだけ 強くなれるかな}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.20,0:26:15.07,Song,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the more I worry, the stronger I become?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.24,0:26:20.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if we're apart, we can just say {離れていてもくちびるで\N確かなこと\Nひとつずつ伝えていけばいいさ}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:20.58,0:26:23.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Things we know for certain
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.08,0:26:29.42,Song,,0,0,0,,one by one with our lips
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.41,0:26:33.09,Song,,0,0,0,,Feelin' future sight {Feelin' future sight\N胸に深く\N打ち寄せる波が\Nridin' on ridin' out 呼びさます\NCallin' birth of light\N哀しみさえ\N溶かすよ きみの 瞳で...}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.80,0:26:36.72,Song,,0,0,0,,The waves crashing
Dialogue: 10,0:26:37.96,0:26:42.06,Song,,0,0,0,,deep in my heart
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.06,0:26:45.73,Song,,0,0,0,,Ridin' on ridin' out I call out to you
Dialogue: 10,0:26:45.73,0:26:48.23,Song,,0,0,0,,Callin' birth of light
Dialogue: 10,0:26:49.24,0:26:52.03,Song,,0,0,0,,Even sadness
Dialogue: 10,0:26:53.07,0:27:00.37,Song,,0,0,0,,will melt away in your eyes
Dialogue: 10,0:27:27.23,0:27:30.05,Song,,0,0,0,,Searchin' angel night
Dialogue: 10,0:27:30.94,0:27:33.57,Song,,0,0,0,,Behind the door,
Dialogue: 10,0:27:34.95,0:27:42.71,Song,,0,0,0,,the hidden love\NFlyin' on flyin' out, it's awakening
Dialogue: 10,0:27:42.71,0:27:45.21,Song,,0,0,0,,Callin' birth of light
